data.description:
MUST SEE!!! This is an excellent 2 bed 2 full bath luxury condo in an unbeatable location. Walking distance to target, hundreds of restaurants and bars, grocery stores, skyway, and all 3 sports stadiums! Luxury Vinyl Plank flooring, massive walk in primary closet, dual vanity, oversized soaking tub, stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, private balcony, heated indoor parking space included, reserved heated storage locker, and new high efficiency in-unit full size washer & dryer to name a few! 

Amenities Galore!!!! Brand new high end state of the art fitness center, yoga center, media center, game room, hot tub, sauna, rooftop patio, dog park, and 24-7 front desk secured attendant in lobby.
